302
00:22:44,222 --> 00:22:50,630
ÇOK! BETHANY'İ DE SİKEYİM, HAVALI AİLESİNİ DE, HAZEL'İ DE SİKEYİM -- SENİ DE!

303
00:23:13,370 --> 00:23:15,023
